'''Equipment''' in Dragon Warrior II includes weapons, armor, shields, and helmets for the three party members.

== Equipment by Character ==

=== Prince of Lorasia ===
The hero can use the widest variety of equipment:
* Most weapons
* Heavy armor
* All shields
* All helmets

=== Prince of Cannock ===
Balanced character with moderate equipment options:
* Light-medium weapons
* Light-medium armor
* Most shields
* Most helmets

=== Princess of Moonbrooke ===
Magic-focused with limited equipment:
* Staffs and wands
* Robes and light armor
* Cannot use shields
* Light helmets only

