== Erdrick's Equipment ==

The legendary equipment set from Dragon Quest I returns:
* '''Erdrick's Sword''' - Cave of Rendarak (+40 Attack)
* '''Erdrick's Armor''' - Hargon's Castle (+35 Defense)
* '''Erdrick's Shield''' - Wellgarth region (+25 Defense)
* '''Erdrick's Helm''' - Tower of the Moon (+20 Defense)

== Cursed Equipment ==

Be cautious of cursed items:
* '''Sword of Destruction''' - High attack but cursed, cannot unequip
* '''Armor of Hades''' - High defense but cursed
* Visit a church to remove cursed items

== Equipment Tips ==

'''Lorasia:'''
* Focus on heavy equipment
* Erdrick's set is ultimate goal
* Falcon Sword good for damage

'''Cannock:'''
* Balance between physical and magic support
* Water Flying Cloth for mobility

'''Moonbrooke:'''
* Magic is primary offense
* Equipment is support only
* Focus gold on princes' equipment

